  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Associated domains establish a secure association between domains and your app so",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "you can share credentials or provide features in your app from your website. For",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "example, an online retailer may offer an app to accompany their website and enhance",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the user experience.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Shared web credentials, universal links, Handoff, and App Clips all use associated",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "domains. Associated domains provide the underpinning to universal links, a feature",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "that allows an app to present content in place of all or part of its website. Users",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "who don’t download the app get the same information in a web browser instead of the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "native app.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To associate a website with your app, you need to have the associated domain file",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "on your website and the appropriate entitlement in your app. The apps in the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "apple-app-site-association",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "file on your website must have a matching ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/BundleResources/Entitlements/com.apple.developer.associated-domains",
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Add the associated domain file to your website",
          "type": "heading",
          "anchor": "Add-the-associated-domain-file-to-your-website",
          "level": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When a user installs your app, the system attempts to download the associated domain",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "file and verify the domains in your entitlement.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "If your site uses multiple subdomains (such as "
                },
                {
                  "code": "example.com",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ", "
                },
                {
                  "code": "www.example.com",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ","
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "and "
                },
                {
                  "code": "support.example.com",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "), each requires its own entry in the "
                },
                {
                  "isActive": true,
                  "type": "reference",
                  "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/BundleResources/Entitlements/com.apple.developer.associated-domains"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": ","
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "and each must serve its own "
                },
                {
                  "code": "apple-app-site-association",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " file."
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "name": "Note",
          "type": "aside",
          "style": "note"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To add the associated domain file to your website, create a file named ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "apple-app-site-association",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "(without an extension). Update the JSON code in the file for the services you",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "support on the domain. For universal links, be sure to list the app identifiers for",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "your domain in the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "applinks",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " service. Similarly, if you create an App Clip, be sure",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to list your App Clip’s app identifier using the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "appclips",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " service.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The following JSON code represents the contents of a simple association file:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "{",
            "  \"applinks\": {",
            "      \"details\": [",
            "           {",
            "             \"appIDs\": [ \"ABCDE12345.com.example.app\", \"ABCDE12345.com.example.app2\" ],",
            "             \"components\": [",
            "               {",
            "                  \"#\": \"no_universal_links\",",
            "                  \"exclude\": true,",
            "                  \"comment\": \"Matches any URL with a fragment that equals no_universal_links and instructs the system not to open it as a universal link.\"",
            "               },",
            "               {",
            "                  \"/\": \"/buy/*\",",
            "                  \"comment\": \"Matches any URL with a path that starts with /buy/.\"",
            "               },",
            "               {",
            "                  \"/\": \"/help/website/*\",",
            "                  \"exclude\": true,",
            "                  \"comment\": \"Matches any URL with a path that starts with /help/website/ and instructs the system not to open it as a universal link.\"",
            "               },",
            "               {",
            "                  \"/\": \"/help/*\",",
            "                  \"?\": { \"articleNumber\": \"????\" },",
            "                  \"comment\": \"Matches any URL with a path that starts with /help/ and that has a query item with name 'articleNumber' and a value of exactly four characters.\"",
            "               }",
            "             ]",
            "           }",
            "       ]",
            "   },",
            "   \"webcredentials\": {",
            "      \"apps\": [ \"ABCDE12345.com.example.app\" ]",
            "   },",
            "",
            "    \"appclips\": {",
            "        \"apps\": [\"ABCDE12345.com.example.MyApp.Clip\"]",
            "    }",
            "}"
          ],
          "type": "codeListing",
          "syntax": "other"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "appIDs"
            },
            {
              "text": " and ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "apps"
            },
            {
              "text": " keys specify the application identifiers for the apps that",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "are available for use on this website along with their service types. Use the following",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "format for the values in these keys:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "<Application Identifier Prefix>.<Bundle Identifier>"
          ],
          "type": "codeListing",
          "syntax": "javascript"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "details",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " dictionary only applies to the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/BundleResources/applinks",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "service type; other service types don’t use it. The ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "components",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " key is an array",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "of dictionaries that provides pattern matching for components of the URL.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "After you construct the association file, place it in your site’s ."
            },
            {
              "code": "well-known",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " directory."
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "The file’s URL should match the following format:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "https://<fully qualified domain>/.well-known/apple-app-site-association"
          ],
          "type": "codeListing",
          "syntax": "other"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You must host the file using "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "https://"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " with a valid certificate and with no redirects."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Add the associated domains entitlement to your app",
          "type": "heading",
          "anchor": "Add-the-associated-domains-entitlement-to-your-app",
          "level": 3
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To set up the entitlement in your app, open the target’s Signing & Capabilities",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "tab in Xcode and add the Associated Domains capability. If they’re not already present,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "this step adds the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/BundleResources/Entitlements/com.apple.developer.associated-domains",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to your app and the associated domains feature to your app ID.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "For a single-target watchOS apps, add the Associated Domains capability",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "to the watchOS app target. For watchOS apps with separate WatchKit extensions, you",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": " ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "text": "must add the Associated Domains capability to the WatchKit Extension target.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "Important",
          "type": "aside",
          "style": "important"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To add your domain to the entitlement, click Add (+) at the bottom of the Domains",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "table to add a placeholder domain. Replace the placeholder with the appropriate prefix",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "for the service your app supports and your site’s domain. Make sure to only include",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the desired subdomain and the top-level domain. Don’t include path and query components",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "or a trailing slash (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "/)",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "supporting-associated-domains-1.png",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Add the domains that share credentials with your app. For services other than",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "appclips",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ", you can prefix a domain with ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "*.",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " to match all of its subdomains.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Each domain you specify uses the following format:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "<service>:<fully qualified domain>"
          ],
          "type": "codeListing",
          "syntax": "other"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Starting with macOS 11 and iOS 14, apps no longer send requests for "
            },
            {
              "type": "codeVoice",
              "code": "apple-app-site-association"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "files directly to your web server. Instead, they send these requests to an Apple-managed"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "content delivery network (CDN) dedicated to associated domains."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "While you’re developing your app, if your web server is unreachable from the public",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "internet, you can use the alternate mode feature to bypass the CDN and connect directly",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to your private domain.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You enable an alternate mode by adding a query string to your associated domain’s"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "entitlement as follows:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "<service>:<fully qualified domain>?mode=<alternate mode>"
          ],
          "type": "codeListing",
          "syntax": "other"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For more information about alternate modes, see "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/BundleResources/Entitlements/com.apple.developer.associated-domains"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For information about universal links, see "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/allowing-apps-and-websites-to-link-to-your-content"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For information about Handoff, see "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Foundation/implementing-handoff-in-your-app"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " "
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "For information about App Clips, see "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/AppClip/configuring-the-launch-experience-of-your-app-clip"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "Apple’s content delivery network requests the ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "type": "codeVoice",
                  "code": "apple-app-site-association"
                },
                {
                  "text": " file for your domain within 24 hours. Devices check for updates approximately once per week after app installation.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "name": "Important",
          "type": "aside",
          "style": "important"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
